{
  "stem": "8703.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What do-- I forgot the name, [INAUDIBLE] his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, it was different because no such thing could be heard-- what I would like-- one-- one man died over there, and they allowed the son to go be-- beyond just the camp and bury him whichever they felt like.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This we couldn't think, even, in barrack C in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing there, they were killing and the family didn't even know what they did with and how he died, how the people died over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and like I said, we were already entirely different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We didn't have-- one thing we didn't have was the Ukrainian [INAUDIBLE], the [INAUDIBLE], that we suffered mostly from them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And number two, we didn't have the sadists, the Polish foremens, that they-- that they were beating us up always.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was-- whatever they had, all the Germans, that they were-- that they were working in the factories in Skarzysko, in Skarzysk, they brought over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And instead of being big shots over there in Skarzysk, they gave them-- the leader of [INAUDIBLE] was a cripple.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], whatever his name was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Over there, they gave him only about five people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You should go and watch them, how they work over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they saw-- the beatings stopped over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The beating for nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, this way they-- they were working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once it was an explosion, a sabotage act.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who did the sabotage act?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a lot of Jewish people-- Jewish prisoners-- were wounded and died under this-- due-- due to the sabotage act.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And over there-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] over there, I had much better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working in the barracks with my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
